397
00:34:38,500 --> 00:34:41,500
Je ne comprend rien à ce que tu racontes.

398
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:50,000
Je crois que si.

399
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:06,600
Dis moi, Lana,

400
00:35:07,100 --> 00:35:10,100
